case.name: Favorite Fairy Tale
case.description: This can be a fairy tale that is known in real life (ex: Little Red Riding Hood, Goldilocks) or one that is prominent in that character's universe.

notes.note: Thank you for the kind message about Fischl being one of Perona's favorite characters! It made me really happy to see. I'll make sure to send more lines towards you. :)
She's mainly embarrassed about how bold she is-- she's not used to girls being bold.

markers.marker: Fischl asks everyone what their favorite fairy tale is.
